# Read `ai/AGENT.md` Before Coding

Before making any code edits in this repository, first read `ai/AGENT.md` in the current session and follow it as the primary local guideline.

If `ai/AGENT.md` has not been read yet in this session, do not proceed with file edits until it is read.
